It's old schooled so it is hard, but there is a few bugs there should be fixed in gameplay. For example objects let my character going, even he should be blocked. Can't wait for new updates. Also boof in the middle of big screen is kinda hard to tap while playing (it's to far). Maybe better it will be to put it above other one?

It's a neat game but it is WAY too difficult. I've played it quite a bit and haven't been able to even get past the first check point except once or twice, and the next time I went to play, I had to start from the beginning of the level. The game is fairly unforgiving since you're always in motion, if you were able to control when your character moved, the platforming portions would be much more manageable. Also the control buttons are locked in the farthest corners of the screen.
In concept its great and music is great but in terms of gameplay its bad. You are forced to move with no directional pad i wish the best with this project but i personally cannot play this.
Dont like how u are forced to walk..a derctional pad would have been nice...
Game itself is super fun but it runs like trash. Phone has 8gb of ram and a mode optimized for gaming, no reason a three dollar game should be laggy with spotty chip tunes. Don't waste your money.
